trans-unit.source: Provides data for the <see cref="E:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.DisplayModeChanging" /> cancelable event.
trans-unit.target: Fornece dados para o evento cancelável <see cref="E:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.DisplayModeChanging" />.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayModeCancelEventArgs> class contains information for the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.DisplayModeChanging> event.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayModeCancelEventArgs> classe contém informações para o <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.DisplayModeChanging> evento.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartEventArgs> class provides access to the display mode that will be applied to the Web Parts control.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartEventArgs> classe fornece acesso para o modo de exibição que será aplicado ao controle de Web Parts.

trans-unit.source: The display mode is accessed through the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayModeCancelEventArgs.NewDisplayMode%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: O modo de exibição é acessado por meio de <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayModeCancelEventArgs.NewDisplayMode%2A> propriedade.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayMode" /> to apply to a Web Parts control.
trans-unit.target: O <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayMode" /> a ser aplicado a um controle de Web Parts.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayModeCancelEventArgs" /> class.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa uma nova instância da classe <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayModeCancelEventArgs" />.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the display mode to apply to a Web Parts control.
trans-unit.target: Obtém ou define o modo de exibição a ser aplicado a um controle de Web Parts.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayMode" /> to apply to a Web Parts control.
trans-unit.target: O <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayMode" /> a ser aplicado a um controle de Web Parts.
